Package io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.core.services.profiler

package io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.core.services.profiler
This package holds classes related to the SlimefunProfiler. The SlimefunProfiler is used to determine Blocks, Chunks or SlimefunItems that cause lag or performance drops.
